# Hydro Ottawa Vendor Security Evaluator

> AI-powered vendor security assessment tool powered by Google Gemini

**Created by:** Desmond Top  
**Last Updated:** February 26, 2026

---

## Overview

The Vendor Security Evaluator is a web-based application that analyzes vendor security documentation (SOC 2 reports, penetration tests, compliance certifications, etc.) using artificial intelligence.

**Key Features:**
- 📄 **Document Analysis** - Upload PDF security reports and documentation
- 🤖 **AI-Powered Evaluation** - Google Gemini API analyzes vendor compliance with customizable security requirements
- 📊 **Interactive Dashboard** - View security scores, requirement breakdowns, and detailed evidence
- ⚙️ **Customizable Settings** - Adjust AI prompts, security requirements, and pass/fail thresholds
- 📈 **Scoring & Simulation** - Compare candidate vendors and analyze what-if scenarios
- 📑 **PDF Reports** - Generate professional security assessment reports

---

