## Troubleshooting

### "GEMINI_API_KEY is missing"
- Ensure `.env` file exists in project root
- Verify `GEMINI_API_KEY=` line is present and not commented out
- Check no trailing/leading spaces in key

### "Database locked" error
- Close any other Python processes using the database
- Ensure no other instances of the app are running
- Try restarting the application

### PDF extraction fails
- Verify PDF files are valid/readable
- Check file permissions
- Check disk space in Storage/ directory

### Streamlit widget not updating
- Refresh browser page (Ctrl+R or Cmd+R)
- Check browser console for JavaScript errors
- Clear Streamlit cache: `streamlit cache clear`

### AI evaluation returns incomplete results
- Check that all required requirements are defined in `requirements.json`
- Verify Gemini API quota isn't exceeded
- Check API key has appropriate permissions

